query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year = 1998 AND t.title LIKE '%Money%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN (SELECT lt.id AS lt_id, ml.link_type_id AS ml_link_type_id, ml.movie_id AS ml_movie_id FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follows%') AS lt_ml ON lt_ml.ml_movie_id = t.id AND lt_ml.ml_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND lt_ml.ml_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year > 1950 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NOT NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind <> 'production companies' AND ct.kind IS NOT NULL JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword IN ('sequel', 'revenge', 'based-on-novel')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2008 JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Drama', 'Horror') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_type_id AS mc_company_type_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id, ct.id AS ct_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]') AS cn_ct_mc ON t.id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id AND cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2008 JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Drama', 'Horror') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'bottom 10 rank' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE 'Birdemic%' OR t.title LIKE '%Movie%') JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind IS NOT NULL AND (ct.kind = 'production companies' OR ct.kind = 'distributors') JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN (SELECT mi.info_type_id AS mi_info_type_id, mi.movie_id AS mi_movie_id, it1.id AS it1_id FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'budget') AS it1_mi ON t.id = it1_mi.mi_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it1_mi.mi_movie_id AND it1_mi.mi_movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
label: 12b

subquery: Hash Join (mi.info_type_id = it1.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'bottom 10 rank' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE 'Birdemic%' OR t.title LIKE '%Movie%') JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind IS NOT NULL AND (ct.kind = 'production companies' OR ct.kind = 'distributors') JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it1 ON mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'budget'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info > '7.0' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Drama', 'Horror', 'Western', 'Family') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_type_id AS mc_company_type_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id, ct.id AS ct_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]') AS cn_ct_mc ON t.id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id AND cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info > '7.0' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Drama', 'Horror', 'Western', 'Family') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS miidx JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = miidx.info_type_id AND it.info = 'rating' JOIN title AS t ON miidx.movie_id = t.id JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_type_id AS mc_company_type_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id, ct.id AS ct_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[de]') AS cn_ct_mc ON cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id = t.id AND miidx.movie_id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi.info_type_id AS mi_info_type_id, mi.movie_id AS mi_movie_id FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'release dates') AS it2_mi ON it2_mi.mi_movie_id = t.id AND it2_mi.mi_movie_id = miidx.movie_id AND it2_mi.mi_movie_id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id

subquery: Hash Join (mc.company_id = cn.id) <- [Hash Join (mc.company_type_id = ct.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_companies, Seq Scan :: company_type], Seq Scan :: company_name]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS miidx JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = miidx.info_type_id AND it.info = 'rating' JOIN title AS t ON miidx.movie_id = t.id JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON mc.movie_id = t.id AND miidx.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[de]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND mi.movie_id = miidx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS miidx JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = miidx.info_type_id AND it.info = 'rating' JOIN title AS t ON miidx.movie_id = t.id AND t.title <> '' AND (t.title LIKE '%Champion%' OR t.title LIKE '%Loser%') JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_type_id AS mc_company_type_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id, ct.id AS ct_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]') AS cn_ct_mc ON cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id = t.id AND miidx.movie_id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi.info_type_id AS mi_info_type_id, mi.movie_id AS mi_movie_id FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'release dates') AS it2_mi ON it2_mi.mi_movie_id = t.id AND it2_mi.mi_movie_id = miidx.movie_id AND it2_mi.mi_movie_id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id

subquery: Hash Join (mi.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS miidx JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = miidx.info_type_id AND it.info = 'rating' JOIN title AS t ON miidx.movie_id = t.id AND t.title <> '' AND (t.title LIKE 'Champion%' OR t.title LIKE 'Loser%') JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON mc.movie_id = t.id AND miidx.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND mi.movie_id = miidx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'release dates'

subquery: Hash Join (mi.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS miidx JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = miidx.info_type_id AND it.info = 'rating' JOIN title AS t ON miidx.movie_id = t.id JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON mc.movie_id = t.id AND miidx.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND mi.movie_id = miidx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS miidx JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = miidx.info_type_id AND it.info = 'rating' JOIN title AS t ON miidx.movie_id = t.id JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_type_id AS mc_company_type_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id, ct.id AS ct_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]') AS cn_ct_mc ON cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id = t.id AND miidx.movie_id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi.info_type_id AS mi_info_type_id, mi.movie_id AS mi_movie_id FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'release dates') AS it2_mi ON it2_mi.mi_movie_id = t.id AND it2_mi.mi_movie_id = miidx.movie_id AND it2_mi.mi_movie_id = cn_ct_mc.mc_movie_id

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info > '6.0' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2010 AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%' OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%' OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%') JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'War') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM aka_name AS an JOIN name AS n ON n.id = an.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON n.id = ci.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN (SELECT mi.info_type_id AS mi_info_type_id, mi.movie_id AS mi_movie_id, it.id AS it_id FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates') AS it_mi ON t.id = it_mi.mi_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it_mi.mi_movie_id AND it_mi.mi_movie_id = ci.movie_id

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM aka_name AS an JOIN name AS n ON n.id = an.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON n.id = ci.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1950 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'sequel', 'second-part', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name NOT LIKE '%Sherlock%' AND (chn.name LIKE '%Tony%Stark%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Iron%Man%') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1950 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'sequel', 'second-part', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name NOT LIKE '%Sherlock%' AND (chn.name LIKE '%Tony%Stark%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Iron%Man%') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'sequel', 'second-part', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN (SELECT n.id AS n_id, ci.person_role_id AS ci_person_role_id, ci.movie_id AS ci_movie_id, ci.person_id AS ci_person_id, chn.id AS chn_id FROM cast_info AS ci JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name LIKE '%Downey%Robert%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name NOT LIKE '%Sherlock%' AND (chn.name LIKE '%Tony%Stark%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Iron%Man%')) AS chn_ci_n ON t.id = chn_ci_n.ci_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = chn_ci_n.ci_movie_id AND chn_ci_n.ci_movie_id = cc.movie_id

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'sequel', 'second-part', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name LIKE '%Downey%Robert%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name NOT LIKE '%Sherlock%' AND (chn.name LIKE '%Tony%Stark%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Iron%Man%')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'sequel', 'second-part', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN (SELECT n.id AS n_id, ci.person_role_id AS ci_person_role_id, ci.movie_id AS ci_movie_id, ci.person_id AS ci_person_id, chn.id AS chn_id FROM cast_info AS ci JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name LIKE '%Downey%Robert%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name NOT LIKE '%Sherlock%' AND (chn.name LIKE '%Tony%Stark%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Iron%Man%')) AS chn_ci_n ON t.id = chn_ci_n.ci_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = chn_ci_n.ci_movie_id AND chn_ci_n.ci_movie_id = cc.movie_id

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German')

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Germany', 'German')

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2010 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'English')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '7.0') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Germany', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '7.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Germany', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '7.0') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Germany', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '7.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Germany', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2009 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '7.0') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Germany', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2009 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '7.0') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Germany', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '8.5') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '8.5') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mk.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]'

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]'

subquery: Hash Join (cc.status_id = cct1.id) <- [Seq Scan :: complete_cast, Seq Scan :: comp_cast_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'release dates' AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%' AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie') JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.status_id AND cct1.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('nerd', 'loner', 'alienation', 'dignity')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'release dates' AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%' AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1990 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'tv movie', 'video movie', 'video game') JOIN (SELECT cc.movie_id AS cc_movie_id, cc.status_id AS cc_status_id, cct1.id AS cct1_id FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.status_id AND cct1.kind = 'complete+verified') AS cc_cct1 ON t.id = cc_cct1.cc_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc_cct1.cc_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc_cct1.cc_movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc_cct1.cc_movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id

subquery: Hash Join (cc.status_id = cct1.id) <- [Seq Scan :: complete_cast, Seq Scan :: comp_cast_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'release dates' AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%' AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1990 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'tv movie', 'video movie', 'video game') JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.status_id AND cct1.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2010 AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('hero', 'martial-arts', 'hand-to-hand-combat', 'computer-animated-movie')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2010 AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('hero', 'martial-arts', 'hand-to-hand-combat', 'computer-animated-movie') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info = 'Horror' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info = 'Horror' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2010 AND t.title LIKE 'Vampire%' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info = 'Horror' JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'War') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '7.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence', 'magnet', 'web', 'claw', 'laser')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name IS NOT NULL AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id
label: 26a

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '7.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence', 'magnet', 'web', 'claw', 'laser') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name IS NOT NULL AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'fight')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name IS NOT NULL AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence', 'magnet', 'web', 'claw', 'laser') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name IS NOT NULL AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000 JOIN (SELECT cct2.id AS cct2_id, cc.subject_id AS cc_subject_id, cc.movie_id AS cc_movie_id, cc.status_id AS cc_status_id, cct1.id AS cct1_id FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew')) AS cc_cct1_cct2 ON t.id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German')

subquery: Hash Join (cc.subject_id = cct1.id) <- [Hash Join (cc.status_id = cct2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: complete_cast, Seq Scan :: comp_cast_type], Seq Scan :: comp_cast_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000 JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000 JOIN (SELECT cct2.id AS cct2_id, cc.subject_id AS cc_subject_id, cc.movie_id AS cc_movie_id, cc.status_id AS cc_status_id, cct1.id AS cct1_id FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew')) AS cc_cct1_cct2 ON t.id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German')

subquery: ~Hash Join~ (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [~Seq Scan~ :: movie_keyword, ~Seq Scan~ :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000 JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year = 1998 JOIN (SELECT cct2.id AS cct2_id, cc.subject_id AS cc_subject_id, cc.movie_id AS cc_movie_id, cc.status_id AS cc_status_id, cct1.id AS cct1_id FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew')) AS cc_cct1_cct2 ON t.id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German')

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t ON ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2010 JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE 'complete%' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL JOIN company_type AS ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' JOIN company_name AS cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON mi.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'English')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '8.5') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '8.5') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '6.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '6.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '8.5') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx.info < '8.5') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
