subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN (SELECT it3.id AS it3_id, pi.info_type_id AS pi_info_type_id, pi.person_id AS pi_person_id FROM person_info AS pi JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia') AS it3_pi ON n.id = it3_pi.pi_person_id AND ci.person_id = it3_pi.pi_person_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

subquery: Hash Join (pi.info_type_id = it3.id) <- [Seq Scan :: person_info, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN person_info AS pi ON n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN (SELECT it3.id AS it3_id, pi.info_type_id AS pi_info_type_id, pi.person_id AS pi_person_id FROM person_info AS pi JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia') AS it3_pi ON n.id = it3_pi.pi_person_id AND ci.person_id = it3_pi.pi_person_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN person_info AS pi ON n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2005 JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN (SELECT it3.id AS it3_id, pi.info_type_id AS pi_info_type_id, pi.person_id AS pi_person_id FROM person_info AS pi JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'height') AS it3_pi ON n.id = it3_pi.pi_person_id AND ci.person_id = it3_pi.pi_person_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%' JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

subquery: Hash Join (pi.info_type_id = it3.id) <- [Seq Scan :: person_info, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2005 JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN person_info AS pi ON n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'height' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%' JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2005 JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN (SELECT it3.id AS it3_id, pi.info_type_id AS pi_info_type_id, pi.person_id AS pi_person_id FROM person_info AS pi JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'height') AS it3_pi ON n.id = it3_pi.pi_person_id AND ci.person_id = it3_pi.pi_person_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%' JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.title = 'Shrek 2' AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2005 JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name = 'Queen' JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN person_info AS pi ON n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'height' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%' JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN (SELECT it3.id AS it3_id, pi.info_type_id AS pi_info_type_id, pi.person_id AS pi_person_id FROM person_info AS pi JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia') AS it3_pi ON n.id = it3_pi.pi_person_id AND ci.person_id = it3_pi.pi_person_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

subquery: Hash Join (pi.info_type_id = it3.id) <- [Seq Scan :: person_info, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN person_info AS pi ON n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation') AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN (SELECT it3.id AS it3_id, pi.info_type_id AS pi_info_type_id, pi.person_id AS pi_person_id FROM person_info AS pi JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia') AS it3_pi ON n.id = it3_pi.pi_person_id AND ci.person_id = it3_pi.pi_person_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id JOIN person_info AS pi ON n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE '%Freddy%' OR t.title LIKE '%Jason%' OR t.title LIKE 'Saw%') JOIN (SELECT cct2.id AS cct2_id, cc.subject_id AS cc_subject_id, cc.movie_id AS cc_movie_id, cc.status_id AS cc_status_id, cct1.id AS cct1_id FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew')) AS cc_cct1_cct2 ON t.id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE '%Freddy%' OR t.title LIKE '%Jason%' OR t.title LIKE 'Saw%') JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE '%Freddy%' OR t.title LIKE '%Jason%' OR t.title LIKE 'Saw%') JOIN (SELECT cct2.id AS cct2_id, cc.subject_id AS cc_subject_id, cc.movie_id AS cc_movie_id, cc.status_id AS cc_status_id, cct1.id AS cct1_id FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew')) AS cc_cct1_cct2 ON t.id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc_cct1_cct2.cc_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE '%Freddy%' OR t.title LIKE '%Jason%' OR t.title LIKE 'Saw%') JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'War') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'War') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%') AS cn_mc ON t.id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%') AS cn_mc ON t.id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE '%Freddy%' OR t.title LIKE '%Jason%' OR t.title LIKE 'Saw%') JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note LIKE '%(Blu-ray)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%' JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

subquery: Hash Join (mk.keyword_id = k.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_keyword, Seq Scan :: keyword]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 AND (t.title LIKE '%Freddy%' OR t.title LIKE '%Jason%' OR t.title LIKE 'Saw%') JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note LIKE '%(Blu-ray)%' JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Thriller') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'War') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx.info_type_id AS mi_idx_info_type_id, mi_idx.movie_id AS mi_idx_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes') AS it2_mi_idx ON t.id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id JOIN (SELECT k.id AS k_id, mk.movie_id AS mk_movie_id, mk.keyword_id AS mk_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital')) AS k_mk ON t.id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id JOIN (SELECT cn.id AS cn_id, mc.movie_id AS mc_movie_id, mc.company_id AS mc_company_id FROM movie_companies AS mc JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%') AS cn_mc ON t.id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND k_mk.mk_movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = it2_mi_idx.mi_idx_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = k_mk.mk_movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cn_mc.mc_movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_info AS mi JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Horror', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'War') JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mi.movie_id JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'violence', 'blood', 'gore', 'death', 'female-nudity', 'hospital') JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.name LIKE 'Lionsgate%' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)', '(head writer)', '(written by)', '(story)', '(story editor)') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN (SELECT mi_idx1.movie_id AS mi_idx1_movie_id, mi_idx1.info_type_id AS mi_idx1_info_type_id, it1.id AS it1_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating') AS it1_mi_idx1 ON t1.id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx2.info_type_id AS mi_idx2_info_type_id, mi_idx2.movie_id AS mi_idx2_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0') AS it2_mi_idx2 ON t2.id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[us]'

subquery: ~Hash Join~ (mi_idx2.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [~Seq Scan~ :: movie_info_idx, ~Seq Scan~ :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 ON t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 ON t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[us]'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN (SELECT mi_idx1.movie_id AS mi_idx1_movie_id, mi_idx1.info_type_id AS mi_idx1_info_type_id, it1.id AS it1_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating') AS it1_mi_idx1 ON t1.id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx2.info_type_id AS mi_idx2_info_type_id, mi_idx2.movie_id AS mi_idx2_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0') AS it2_mi_idx2 ON t2.id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[us]'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx1.info_type_id = it1.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2008 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 ON t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 ON t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[us]'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year = 2007 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN (SELECT mi_idx1.movie_id AS mi_idx1_movie_id, mi_idx1.info_type_id AS mi_idx1_info_type_id, it1.id AS it1_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating') AS it1_mi_idx1 ON t1.id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx2.info_type_id AS mi_idx2_info_type_id, mi_idx2.movie_id AS mi_idx2_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0') AS it2_mi_idx2 ON t2.id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[nl]'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx2.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year = 2007 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 ON t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 ON t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[nl]'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year = 2007 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN (SELECT mi_idx1.movie_id AS mi_idx1_movie_id, mi_idx1.info_type_id AS mi_idx1_info_type_id, it1.id AS it1_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating') AS it1_mi_idx1 ON t1.id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx2.info_type_id AS mi_idx2_info_type_id, mi_idx2.movie_id AS mi_idx2_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0') AS it2_mi_idx2 ON t2.id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[nl]'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx1.info_type_id = it1.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year = 2007 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 ON t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 ON t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.info < '3.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code = '[nl]'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT mi_idx1.movie_id AS mi_idx1_movie_id, mi_idx1.info_type_id AS mi_idx1_info_type_id, it1.id AS it1_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating') AS it1_mi_idx1 ON t1.id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx2.info_type_id AS mi_idx2_info_type_id, mi_idx2.movie_id AS mi_idx2_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx2.info < '3.5') AS it2_mi_idx2 ON t2.id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code <> '[us]'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx2.info_type_id = it2.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 ON t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 ON t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.info < '3.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code <> '[us]'

query_ues: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT mi_idx1.movie_id AS mi_idx1_movie_id, mi_idx1.info_type_id AS mi_idx1_info_type_id, it1.id AS it1_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating') AS it1_mi_idx1 ON t1.id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id JOIN (SELECT it2.id AS it2_id, mi_idx2.info_type_id AS mi_idx2_info_type_id, mi_idx2.movie_id AS mi_idx2_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx2.info < '3.5') AS it2_mi_idx2 ON t2.id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code <> '[us]'

subquery: Hash Join (mi_idx1.info_type_id = it1.id) <- [Seq Scan :: movie_info_idx, Seq Scan :: info_type]
query_ues_linear: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 ON t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 ON t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.info < '3.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code <> '[us]'
